ONS Best-fit 2021 Output Areas (OA) to 2023 Wards

Trafford

The maps below present the Trafford 2023 wards (black line) and the corresponding 2021 OAs (purple areas) that best fit each ward according to the ONS best-fit lookup. OAs are the smallest geography used by ONS to publish Census 2021 results.
